title: Belarus defies sanctions, seeks economic union and broad global alliances
description: In the face of growing international sanctions, Belarus has defiantly charted a new course, building its economic fortitude and strengthening ties with major multinational organizations. President Alexander Lukashenko proclaimed this plan of action at the Supreme Eurasian Economic Council meeting in Moscow, with an underlying ambition to cultivate a comprehensive economic union void of barriers ... title: Temasek reduces compensation for staff responsible for botched FTX investment
description: Singapore-based investment firm, Temasek Holdings, has cut down the compensation of its executives responsible for the failed investment in the now-bankrupt crypto exchange, FTX.
